author: michele.mostarda
msg: Integrated RDFa 1.1 Extractor in ExtractorRegistry, couple of tests fixed to be compliant with the new default extractor. Added backward compatibility to the RDFa 1.0 XSLT based Extractor via the 'any23.extraction.rdfa.programmatic' configuration flag.

author: michele.mostarda
msg: This branch has been merged in trunk at revision r1544.

author: michele.mostarda
msg: The RDFa 1.1 Extractor test cases have been extended from a common test base
with the existing RDFa 1.0 Extractor based on XSLT. The common test base
Some test cases for RDFa 1.0 have been adapted to be compatible with RDFa 1.1.
- Major refactoring of AbstractExtractorTestCase.java with the adaptation
of the extending classes. The AbstractExtractorTestCase.java refactoring
has added more methods to inspect Extractor results and verify produced
errors and warnings, as well as some method signature optimizations.

author: michele.mostarda
msg: Added support for RDFa 1.1 @vocab attribute. See http://www.w3.org/TR/rdfa-core/#A-vocab .
